  <description><![CDATA[<p>For an amazing tour that’ll visit all the hot spots, join this Circle of Iceland escorted tour. Getting to experience all the nature, culture and history that this amazing country has to offer. Complete with volcanoes, lava fields, hot springs, mountains, fjords, glacier lagoon and waterfalls.</p>
<p><strong>Maximum Group Size: 30</strong></p>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/circle-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/circle-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Itinerary">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/circle-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/circle-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Hotels">Hotels </a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-iceland/circle-of-iceland-escorted-tour#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
